   United States v. Corona-Sanchez, 98-50452
   Three-Judge Panel Opinion: 234 F.3d 449 (9th Cir. 2000)
   Order Taking Case En Banc: 265 F.3d 1079 (9th Cir. 2001)
   Date of Order Taking Case En Banc: September 14, 2001
   Status: Argued and submitted December 11, 2001, 8:30 a.m., Pasadena
   Members of En Banc Court: Mary M. Schroeder, Stephen R. Reinhardt, Alex
   Kozinski, Pamela A. Rymer, Thomas G. Nelson, Andrew J. Kleinfeld,
