   United Food v. NLRB, 99-71317/99-71442/99-71596/00-70156/00-70189
   Three-Judge Panel Opinion: 249 F.3d 1115 (9th Cir. 2001)
   Order Taking Case En Banc: 265 F.3d 1079 (9th Cir. 2001)
   Date of Order Taking Case En Banc: September 14, 2001
   Status: Argued and submitted December 11, 2001, 11:00 a.m., Pasadena
