   Workers violate the National Labor Relations Act by requiring nonmember
   employees to fund the union's organizing activities? Did another Local
   violate the Act by telling new employees that they were required to
   become full members of the Local? Was the National Labor Relations
   Board's remedial order too broad?
   Holding: Not yet decided
