   United States v. Matthews, 98-10499
   Three-Judge Panel Opinion: 240 F.3d 806 (9th Cir. 2001)
   Order Taking Case En Banc: 254 F.3d 825 (9th Cir. 2001)
   Date of Order Taking Case En Banc: June 12, 2001
   Status: Argued and submitted September 24, 2001, 2:00 p.m., San
   Francisco
